      <div class="container-fluid container-testimony">
        <div class="row row-testimony">
          <div class="col-lg-12 col-testimony d-flex">
            <div class="recuadro-testimony">
              <img class="img-testimony" src="/images/artists/testimony.jpg" alt="">
              <h3 class="h3-testimony">"The help I needed"</h3>
              <div class="recuadro-testimony-interior">
                <p>Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Delectus quia voluptatum numquam quod incidunt saepe eveniet unde eius dolorum dolore.</p>
                <a class="btn-general btn-testimony" href="/artist/allArtists">See Our Artists</a>
